<br>
What other class in a Keep take can't get a rez?<br>
<br>
You may like risk, but I don't call that risk, I call running back for 20 minutes so I can fight for 1 minute borring.  Plus, as a kobold, there are some keeps that I can NOT jump out of since I can't get over the walls.  Trying to climb that little climb spot in lag is near impossible.<br>
<br>
Also, now people just sit right next to climb spot and wack you while you are climbing.  They can hit you through the wall before you even get inside.<br>
<br>
Climb was a neat thing when we could get rez, but now it is really not very useful.  Yes you can do a suicide run, or maybe kill one person and get out alive.  But in truth Climb is about as useful as Detect Danger, Distraction and Safe Fall.  All of these &quot;skills&quot; have some use, but the uses are rare and really don't offer much utility.<br>
<br>
There needs to be at least 6 or 8 climb spots on every keep, every race regardless of size should be able to jump over the walls, and Milegates need climb spots.  Until we get more climb spots this &quot;skill&quot; is really not very useful, especially now when just about any class in the game can just lag right through the doors/walls.<br>
<br>
